<section xml:id="S_eyeball_lines">
  <title>Eyeballing Lines of Best Fit</title>

  <subsection>
    <title>Overview</title>
    
    
    <p>
      Sometimes data is not perfectly linear, but has a linear trend. An example follows.
    </p>
  </subsection>

